00:05:12.840 --> 00:05:15.800
The background size can be set to covert to make

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:18.925
the image cover the full background area,

00:05:18.925 --> 00:05:22.900
and then we're going to set the display type to be flex,

00:05:22.900 --> 00:05:25.205
just like we've looked at in the header.

00:05:25.205 --> 00:05:29.315
