00:05:32.545 --> 00:05:35.900
we can now see that the text is now placed on top of

00:05:35.900 --> 00:05:39.905
the image rather than sitting above it, like it was before.

00:05:39.905 --> 00:05:44.030
We can now use the flexbox to align this text in the center,

00:05:44.030 --> 00:05:46.495
both horizontally and vertically.

00:05:46.495 --> 00:05:48.979
To set the text line as vertically,

00:05:48.979 --> 00:05:52.380
we can set the line items property.

00:05:52.810 --> 00:05:56.225
Let's add this just below the display type.

00:05:56.225 --> 00:06:00.835
Align items into the center,

00:06:00.835 --> 00:06:03.090
and let's take a look at this.

00:06:03.090 --> 00:06:08.425
Refresh. Now we can see that this is aligned vertically to the image.

00:06:08.425 --> 00:06:10.880
Now, to send the text horizontally,

00:06:10.880 --> 00:06:21.750
we can use another flexbox property of justify content and also set this to be sensor,

00:06:21.750 --> 00:06:25.140
so save and give that refresh.

00:06:25.140 --> 00:06:29.720
Now we can see the text has now moved into the middle of the image.

